config BR2_PACKAGE_RPI5_SECURITY_INIT
    bool "rpi5-security-init"
    depends on BR2_INIT_SYSTEMD
    depends on BR2_PACKAGE_TPM2_TOOLS
    help
      First-boot TPM 2.0 provisioning and platform attestation
      initialization service for Raspberry Pi 5.

      Performs:
        - TPM ownership taking and EK certificate provisioning
        - AIK (Attestation Identity Key) generation
        - Initial PCR policy sealing
        - Disk encryption key unsealing
